OL,3,CCornwall Council 'could go bust in two
OL,4,Cyears' without extra funding
OL,6,FThe deputy leader of Cornwall Council
OL,7,Fhas warned the authority could "go
OL,8,Fbust" within the next two years and
OL,9,Ffaces a "financial abyss" without
OL,10,Fextra government funding.JOn Tuesday
OL,11,F20 February, councillors debated
OL,12,Fincreasing council tax by almost five
OL,13,Fper cent - the maximum allowed without
OL,14,Ftriggering a referendum - but even
OL,15,Fthat may not be enough to balance the
OL,16,Fbooks.JCllr David Harris, Conservative
OL,17,Fdeputy leader who is responsible for
OL,18,Ffinance, urged his colleagues to
OL,19,F"scream properly" at politicians in
OL,20,FWestminster, adding: "If we don't get
OL,21,Fa radical review, we will be bust
OL,22,Finside two years".
