OL,3,CCornwall Council 'could go bust in two
OL,4,Cyears' without extra funding
OL,6,FThe council has a budget shortfall of
OL,7,F#14million, which will be taken out of
OL,8,Freserves.
OL,10,FDemand for services is outstripping
OL,11,Fincome, with particular pressure on
OL,12,Fchildren in care; school transport;
OL,13,Fand temporary and emergency
OL,14,Faccommodation for homeless people.
OL,16,FCllr Colin Martin, Liberal Democrat
OL,17,Fleader, branded the budget "a
OL,18,Fdisaster" and accused the
OL,19,FConservatives of taking "political
OL,20,Fchoices" and "losing control".
