OL,3,CCornwall Council 'could go bust in two
OL,4,Cyears' without extra funding
OL,6,FThe council will be allowed to
OL,7,Fincrease council tax on second homes,
OL,8,Fbut this will not come into force
OL,9,Funtil April 2025.
OL,11,FCllr Dick Cole, of Mebyon Kernow, said
OL,12,Fthere is "no option" other than to
OL,13,Fmake cuts, use reserves and increase
OL,14,Fcouncil tax, but added the county
OL,15,F"should not be in this position".
