OL,3,CCornwall Council 'could go bust in two
OL,4,Cyears' without extra funding
OL,6,FLabour leader Cllr Jayne Kirkham said:
OL,7,F"We have moved the burden to the
OL,8,Fpeople least able to cope. Council tax
OL,9,Fis an unfair tax. Householders in
OL,10,FCornwall pay more than people who own
OL,11,Fvery expensive properties in other
OL,12,Fareas of the country. We have more
OL,13,Fpoverty and we don't get the help from
OL,14,Fcentral government for that."
OL,16,FAlmost every local council with
OL,17,Fresponsibility for social care in
OL,18,FEngland plans to raise its council tax
OL,19,Fby the maximum this April, according
OL,20,Fto data compiled by the County
OL,21,FCouncils Network (CCN).
